  "remarks": "CDi.005 Former President of UCD/FAPC. Given the rank of General in the FARDC in December 2004. As of June 2011 detained in Makala Prison in Kinshasa. On 25 March 2011, the High Military Court in Kinshasa opened a trial against Kakwavu for war crimes. In November 2014, convicted by a DRC military court to ten years in prison for rape, murder, and torture.; Listing: Listed by 1533 Committee 1 Nov. 2005",
